premonition.

00:11.679 --> 00:13.914
-Love those omens.
-Go, Billy!

00:17.017 --> 00:20.088
Oh, no.
It finally happened.

00:20.188 --> 00:22.056
Klaus got
the lunch lady job.

00:22.156 --> 00:23.591
Next.

00:23.691 --> 00:25.926
Oh, Steve!
It's me, Klaus!

00:26.026 --> 00:27.628
You know, from home?

00:27.728 --> 00:29.097
Oh, God,
don't talk to me.

00:29.197 --> 00:30.598
Come here, honey.

00:30.698 --> 00:33.467
I saved you the crustiest
corner of mac and cheese.

00:33.567 --> 00:35.569
It's so hard.

00:36.270 --> 00:37.638
Steve, I know
I should know this,

00:37.738 --> 00:39.540
but how are you
related to Klaus?

00:39.640 --> 00:41.075
I thought
they were a couple!

00:41.175 --> 00:42.943
I don't want to talk
about Klaus anymore.

00:43.043 --> 00:43.944
I can't even eat.

00:44.044 --> 00:45.246
(sniffs)

00:45.346 --> 00:46.947
Is someone having
Crepes Suzette?

00:47.047 --> 00:49.317
Ugh,
the hall monitors.

00:49.417 --> 00:51.252
I hate how they get
special treatment.

00:51.352 --> 00:52.320
Come on.

00:52.420 --> 00:55.289
Principal Lewis takes
troubled kids from juvie

00:55.389 --> 00:58.292
and molds them into
productive members of society.

00:58.392 --> 00:59.760
Yeah, they made
the cover

00:59.860 --> 01:02.663
of Appropriate Relationships
Magazine.

01:04.498 --> 01:05.433
