the sawdust absorbs the puke.

01:22.550 --> 01:24.918
This is why
I became a janitor.

01:25.018 --> 01:27.155
I became a janitor
because it was fate.

01:27.255 --> 01:28.856
As you can see...

01:28.956 --> 01:32.193
