looks somewhat like a mop.

01:32.526 --> 01:34.962
(patriotic music plays)

01:35.062 --> 01:37.631
* Good morning, U.S.A. *

01:37.731 --> 01:41.502
* I got a feelin' that
it's gonna be a wonderful day *

01:41.602 --> 01:44.705
* The sun in the sky
has a smile on his face *

01:44.805 --> 01:49.009
