02:02.590 --> 02:04.492
Well, they fired me.

02:04.592 --> 02:07.027
They blamed me for all
those kids getting sick.

02:07.127 --> 02:08.362
It's ridiculous.

02:08.462 --> 02:09.963
I always said "excuse me"

02:10.063 --> 02:12.166
