a lunch lady.

02:19.673 --> 02:21.642
I was the eighth one
fired this year.

02:21.742 --> 02:23.911
Eighth...third.

02:24.011 --> 02:25.579
That's a lot of numbers.

02:25.679 --> 02:28.015
Maybe we should go take
a look around the cafeteria.

02:28.115 --> 02:33.987
**

02:34.087 --> 02:36.390
Whoa.
Sawdust.

02:36.490 --> 02:38.726
Hmm...

02:38.826 --> 02:41.829
Whoa.
Sawdust.

02:41.929 --> 02:43.197
Hmm...

02:43.297 --> 02:47.535
**

02:47.635 --> 02:48.769
