02:48.869 --> 02:50.338
No sawdust.

02:50.438 --> 02:51.939
Or is it?

02:52.039 --> 02:53.040
What do you mean?

02:53.140 --> 02:55.175
I don't know.

02:55.876 --> 02:58.212
Just the usual dry-aged beef

02:58.312 --> 03:01.349
