public high school cafeteria.

03:01.449 --> 03:02.750
Unless...

03:04.685 --> 03:05.619
Hmm...

03:05.719 --> 03:06.954
MAN: Hey!
Who's in there?

03:07.054 --> 03:09.757
Hank Turlington,
school detective.

03:09.857 --> 03:10.924
We need to talk.

03:11.024 --> 03:12.626
And you need to walk.

03:12.726 --> 03:15.062
Me and my partner are also
school detectives,

03:15.162 --> 03:16.897
and we're already
on the case.

03:16.997 --> 03:18.966
Maybe we can join...

03:19.066 --> 03:19.967
forces.

03:20.067 --> 03:20.968
Maybe.

03:21.068 --> 03:22.303
Is that a yes?

03:22.403 --> 03:24.238
Yes.
We have joined forces.

03:24.338 --> 03:25.739
Three man handshake?

03:25.839 --> 03:26.774
Yes.

03:26.874 --> 03:27.808
Steve, please join us?

03:27.908 --> 03:28.809
Yes.

03:28.909 --> 03:32.580
**

03:35.115 --> 03:37.385
**

03:37.485 --> 03:40.454
Great idea to start
mall walking, Stan.

03:40.554 --> 03:42.456
Hey, what's the name
of Steve's tailor?

03:42.556 --> 03:44.392
-Petruchio?
-No, his other tailor.

03:44.492 --> 03:45.893
-Carbunkle.
-Yes, that's right.

03:45.993 --> 03:46.960
Hey, Carbunkle!

03:49.597 --> 03:50.664
(creaking, bone cracks)

03:50.764 --> 03:53.401
(screams)

03:59.273 --> 04:01.409
