at Williams Sonoma.

04:04.678 --> 04:06.447
WOMAN: He's coming
back out the top!

04:06.547 --> 04:08.349
(squishing)

04:13.253 --> 04:14.588
Hey there, fellas.
You mall walking?

04:14.688 --> 04:16.089
I've always wanted
to try that out.

04:16.189 --> 04:18.426
Got room for one more?

04:18.526 --> 04:19.827
Guys?

04:19.927 --> 04:21.795
Eh, they're right, Al,
you'd just slow them down.

04:21.895 --> 04:24.532
So smile, you fat clown,
and walk away.

04:24.632 --> 04:26.334
Catch ya next time,
homies!

04:27.701 --> 04:30.137
**

04:30.237 --> 04:32.272
Something strange is
going on at this school,

04:32.373 --> 04:34.375
and it all centers
around Principal Lewis

04:34.475 --> 04:35.543
and the hall monitors.

04:35.643 --> 04:36.710
I've been working
undercover

04:36.810 --> 04:39.313
as social studies teacher
"Mrs. Womanface."

04:39.413 --> 04:41.148
