in charge of

04:41.248 --> 04:42.816
the Sadie Hawkins dance.

04:42.916 --> 04:44.151
This year's theme?

04:44.251 --> 04:45.819
"Everyone Must Get Laid."

04:45.919 --> 04:48.155
So, what can I do?
I-I want to help.

04:48.255 --> 04:49.523
With the sex dance?

04:49.623 --> 04:50.624
Or the school mystery?

04:50.724 --> 04:52.059
The...second thing.

04:52.159 --> 04:54.628
I need someone undercover
in the hall monitors.

04:54.728 --> 04:56.730
Lewis only
recruits bad kids.

04:56.830 --> 04:58.799
So you're about to get
sent to juvie.

05:00.534 --> 05:01.902
(body thuds, punching)

05:02.002 --> 05:05.172
Help!
A student is attacking me!

05:05.272 --> 05:06.640
-(thud)
-Wow.

05:06.740 --> 05:08.909
You think you know
all the things that turn you on,

05:09.009 --> 05:11.044
but then you see
something like this,

05:11.144 --> 05:13.180
and suddenly you're
at half-mast.

05:13.280 --> 05:15.082
Aah!

05:15.182 --> 05:16.650
It was this boy
right here.

05:16.750 --> 05:19.487
He overpowered me,
then he sat down.

05:19.587 --> 05:20.988
**

05:21.088 --> 05:22.055
(inmates "whoo"ing)

05:22.322 --> 05:24.191
TURLINGTON: AJ Slick, the head
of the hall monitors,

05:24.291 --> 05:26.326
has a brother in juvie,
TJ Slick.

05:26.427 --> 05:28.996
I pulled some strings
to make you his cellmate.

05:29.096 --> 05:30.764
That's the easy part.

05:30.864 --> 05:31.999
The hard part's gonna be

05:32.099 --> 05:34.101
getting this monster
to trust you.

05:34.201 --> 05:35.369
Trust fall!

05:36.336 --> 05:37.505
You passed my test.

05:37.605 --> 05:38.872
Now we're friends forever.

05:38.906 --> 05:39.840
(smooches)

05:39.940 --> 05:40.841
**

05:40.941 --> 05:42.443
