in the yard.

05:44.645 --> 05:46.680
**

05:46.780 --> 05:49.082
GUARD: Steve Smith?

05:49.182 --> 05:50.584
You're gettin'
out today.

05:50.684 --> 05:51.852
Already?

05:51.952 --> 05:53.754
I've only been
slamming my gams.

05:53.854 --> 05:55.856
Didn't even get a chance
to jack my sides

05:55.956 --> 05:58.358
or fran my front
or clunk my neck.

06:00.728 --> 06:01.762
Klaus?

06:01.862 --> 06:04.398
