in your pocket.

06:04.498 --> 06:06.033
I've been in this
storage locker

06:06.133 --> 06:09.302
for a month surviving
on leaky AC unit drippings,

06:09.403 --> 06:14.107
rat piss, and, ucch,
coconut LaCroix.

06:14.207 --> 06:17.611
**

06:17.711 --> 06:22.249
Well, well, well,
if it isn't Steve Smith.

06:22.349 --> 06:24.918
Yeah, don't splooge
in your pants or anything.

06:25.018 --> 06:26.454
You wish.

06:26.554 --> 06:30.157
My anti-depressants make that
absolutely impossible.

06:30.257 --> 06:31.959
Told you
this guy's a dork.

06:32.059 --> 06:33.561
I thought that, too.

06:33.661 --> 06:36.296
But I heard you were tight
with my big bro in juvie.

06:36.396 --> 06:39.299
I think Steve should be
our new hall monitor.

06:39.399 --> 06:41.268
Yo, I don't know
about this guy, AJ.

06:41.368 --> 06:42.570
