Would a narc do this?

06:45.338 --> 06:47.007
Oh, hey, Steve.

06:47.107 --> 06:48.241
We miss yo--
Ooh!

06:48.341 --> 06:49.477
Aah!

06:49.577 --> 06:52.513
Aaah!

06:52.613 --> 06:54.114
Sorry!

06:54.214 --> 06:56.517
But I! Have to! Do this!

06:56.617 --> 06:59.687
Cold-blooded, Smith!

06:59.787 --> 07:01.522
Your cruel whispers
that we couldn't hear

07:01.622 --> 07:03.323
really added
insult to injury.

07:03.423 --> 07:05.659
Welcome to
the hall monitors, Smith.

07:05.759 --> 07:06.660
Here's your hat.

07:06.760 --> 07:08.596
Are the fanny packs part
of the uniform?

07:08.696 --> 07:10.598
Nah. They're part
of our bodies.

07:10.698 --> 07:12.165
You'll grow one, too.

07:14.702 --> 07:16.937
**

07:17.037 --> 07:19.673
Steve, forget class.

07:19.773 --> 07:21.274
You're a hall monitor.

07:21.374 --> 07:23.443
Lewis lets us
do whatever we want.

07:23.544 --> 07:24.812
You wanna go to my house
and watch

07:24.912 --> 07:27.615
Wall Street:
Money Never Sleeps on my bed?

07:27.715 --> 07:29.517
Oh, here we go.
Hall pass?

07:29.617 --> 07:30.684
Um...

07:30.784 --> 07:31.885
Aah!

07:31.985 --> 07:34.655
You remind me of a dog turd
I once stepped in.

07:34.755 --> 07:36.890
It got into all the grooves
of my shoe,

07:36.990 --> 07:39.392
and it took my mom weeks
to clean it.

07:39.493 --> 07:41.128
Yeah, Steve! Yeah!

07:41.228 --> 07:43.030
He's hiding something.

07:43.130 --> 07:45.966
Let's see what he's got
in that backpack.

07:46.066 --> 07:47.300
(zipper unzips)

07:47.400 --> 07:48.636
MERTZ: It's everything

07:48.736 --> 07:50.403
we need to make
a spaghetti dinner.

07:50.504 --> 07:52.205
Nice haul, Double S.

07:52.305 --> 07:54.007
Any chance you snagged
a cabernet?

07:54.107 --> 07:56.143
No, but I got
this kid's clarinet.

07:56.243 --> 07:58.011
Clarinet sounds
like cabernet.

07:58.111 --> 08:01.414
