clues for the school mystery,

08:18.498 --> 08:20.601
not becoming
a Richard-Grieco-type bad boy

08:20.701 --> 08:22.335
who plays
by his own rules.

08:22.435 --> 08:24.905
Klaus, I'm fine.
I-I'm undercover.

08:25.005 --> 08:26.106
It's all an act.

08:26.206 --> 08:27.875
I hope so.
You're supposed to be

08:27.975 --> 08:29.577
getting my lunch lady
job back.

08:29.677 --> 08:31.745
And hey, bro,
why you peeing

08:31.845 --> 08:33.747
in the stall
like a shy guy?

08:33.847 --> 08:36.016
Your dick's
super cool.

08:36.116 --> 08:38.018
(bell rings)

08:38.118 --> 08:39.252
PRINCIPAL LEWIS:
You guys sure about

08:39.352 --> 08:40.688
this goody-two-shoes?

08:40.788 --> 08:42.756
I don't trust you,
Smith.

08:42.856 --> 08:45.058
Maybe you need
a little test.

08:45.158 --> 08:46.426
Jerk off in front
of these prudes.

08:46.526 --> 08:48.128
-What?
-Yo, we've been over this.

08:48.228 --> 08:50.931
