and vandalize it.

08:55.636 --> 08:57.037
Why this pet store?

08:57.137 --> 08:59.272
Because years ago,
I bought a pet gecko there

08:59.372 --> 09:00.407
and it bit me.

09:00.507 --> 09:02.943
