on your breath.

09:17.257 --> 09:18.325
Whatever.

09:18.425 --> 09:20.628
It's a slippery slope,
Steve.

09:20.728 --> 09:21.662
First it's cloves.

09:21.762 --> 09:22.663
Then it's e-cigs.

09:22.763 --> 09:23.931
Then it's regular cigs.

09:24.031 --> 09:25.065
Then it's mary jane.

09:25.165 --> 09:26.099
Then it's cocaine.

09:26.199 --> 09:27.735
Then it's
black tar heroin.

09:27.835 --> 09:29.236
That is the order.

09:29.336 --> 09:30.904
You think I like this?

09:31.004 --> 09:33.573
You think I'm enjoying
doing whatever I want

09:33.674 --> 09:36.844
with total impunity,
basically running the school

09:36.944 --> 09:40.013
and being less a student
and more a god?

09:40.113 --> 09:42.850
Pray to me!

09:42.950 --> 09:44.785
Sorry, I missed all that.

09:44.885 --> 09:46.586
The lunch ladies
and I just about had our

09:46.687 --> 09:49.289
escape room night planned,
and now Gretchen wants to change

09:49.389 --> 09:51.524
everything around
for her son's funeral.

09:51.625 --> 09:53.426
I'm not a bad kid.

09:53.526 --> 09:55.963
I just need to gain
Lewis' trust.

09:56.063 --> 09:57.865
I'll only release
one animal.

09:57.965 --> 10:00.533
No harm, no foul,
no big whoop.

10:00.634 --> 10:02.302
(monkey screeching)

10:02.402 --> 10:03.804
No, no, no, no, no, no, no.

10:03.904 --> 10:04.972
No, no, no, no!

10:05.072 --> 10:06.339
Not the snakes!

10:06.439 --> 10:07.374
No!

10:07.474 --> 10:09.009
Oh!

10:09.109 --> 10:11.011
Not the pretty peacocks!

10:11.111 --> 10:12.445
**

10:12.545 --> 10:14.782
(animals roaring, screeching)

10:15.849 --> 10:17.317
STEVE:
I'm sure they'll come back.

10:19.887 --> 10:21.388
-(peacocks squawking)
-How do these stupid birds

10:21.488 --> 10:23.023
