in our house?

10:23.123 --> 10:28.195
Oh, ladies, ladies,
this dancing has exhausted me.

10:28.295 --> 10:31.531
Let us step inside
for some refreshments.

10:31.631 --> 10:33.701
Myah! Myah!

10:33.801 --> 10:34.968
That laugh.

10:35.068 --> 10:36.536
It's enchanting!

10:36.636 --> 10:38.305
(squawking)

10:38.405 --> 10:40.974
Hey, it's that wonderful
working-class Brit

10:41.074 --> 10:42.843
who owns the sunglass place
at the mall.

10:42.943 --> 10:44.577
(British accent)
I found yer 'usband

10:44.678 --> 10:45.713
and this grey boy
at the mall.

10:45.813 --> 10:48.215
Why are they
frozen like this?

10:48.315 --> 10:51.051
These geezas saw
sum'ing terrible.

10:51.151 --> 10:54.421
Sum'ing that made them
lose their words.

10:54.521 --> 10:59.760
