shipment of Oakley's.

11:12.105 --> 11:14.742
-What did he say?
-I think it was a poem.

11:14.842 --> 11:16.944
It was so beautiful.

11:17.044 --> 11:18.678
'Sup with them?

11:18.779 --> 11:21.081
(bell rings)

11:21.181 --> 11:25.085
Today's chicken provencal
was amazing.

11:25.185 --> 11:29.356
